<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-59-0266 </DOCNO><TEXT>Remote operation and monitoring systems, when allied with pump protectionand automatic control, can be readily justified on financial groundsin known water make conditions and normal working conditions. When thewater make risks the whole mine, or when the working conditions are notnormal, as happened during the UK miners' strike, the value of this systemis incalculable. However for such a system to deliver the benefits outlined,it is necessary for a user to thoroughly recognise his need and selecthis system carefully. 3 figs.</TEXT></DOC>